            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6 animate-fade-in text-shadow leading-tight">
              Best & Compare Swiss Health Insurance — 2026 Guide for Expats
            </h1>
            <p class="mt-6 text-xl text-white/95 animate-slide-up text-shadow leading-relaxed">
              Switzerland's healthcare is world-class — choosing the right insurer as a newcomer can be overwhelming. We compare every major provider, explain the rules, and help you register — free of charge.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col items-start gap-4 animate-slide-up">
              <button
                class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 text-white font-bold rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 text-lg"
                onclick="window.openHealthModal('best-compare')"
                aria-label="Compare and get personal advice"
                data-evt="cta_hero_compare"
              >
                Compare & Get Personal Advice
                <svg class="ml-2 h-5 w-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" />
                </svg>
              </button>
              <a href="#how-it-works" class="text-white/90 text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors underline">
                How our consultation works
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================ -->
  <!-- B) QUICK FACTS GRID -->
  <!-- ============================================ -->
  <section class={cn("bg-white", DesignSystem.spacing.section.padding)}>
    <div class={DesignSystem.spacing.container.default}>
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          {quickFacts.map(fact => (
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-md border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-gray-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                  {fact.icon === 'Clock' && (
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                    </svg>
                  )}
                  {fact.icon === 'Shield' && (
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
                    </svg>
                  )}
                  {fact.icon === 'Plus' && (
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4" />
                    </svg>
                  )}
                  {fact.icon === 'TrendingUp' && (
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
                    </svg>
                  )}
                  {fact.icon === 'Calendar' && (
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                    </svg>
                  )}
                  {fact.icon === 'MessageCircle' && (
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z" />
                    </svg>
                  )}
                  {fact.icon === 'Users' && (
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" />
                    </svg>
                  )}
                  {fact.icon === 'Award' && (
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z" />
                    </svg>
                  )}
                  {fact.icon === 'DollarSign' && (
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                    </svg>
                  )}
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 mb-1">{fact.label}</p>
                  <p class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-900">{fact.value}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================ -->
  <!-- C) WHY COMPARISON MATTERS -->
  <!-- ============================================ -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class={DesignSystem.spacing.container.default}>
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
          There Isn't One "Best Insurer" — There's the Best for You
        </h2>
        <div class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-4 text-left">
          <p>
            The right health insurance choice depends on multiple factors: how long you'll stay in Switzerland, your expected health usage, preferred insurance model (Standard / HMO / Telmed), any pre-existing conditions, your budget, and specific benefits like gym rebates or international coverage.
          </p>
          <p>
            Each major insurer — <strong>Swica, Helsana, CSS, Sanitas</strong> — has different acceptance policies, pricing structures, and service strengths. Some use age-entry pricing for supplementary insurance, others adjust annually. Some excel at digital services, others at personal support.
          </p>
          <p>
            That's why we don't recommend one "best" insurer. Instead, we analyze your specific situation during a free consultation and match you with the insurer that truly fits your life in Switzerland.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Expert Quote Block -->
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-12">
        <div class="bg-white border border-red-200 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-md relative">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-red-500 absolute top-4 left-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h4v10h-10z"/>
          </svg>
